  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t美國國會正式通過下個財政年度嘅國防授權預算案，國防預算案內列明中國(包括香港，澳門，新彊)為「海外敵對勢力」，與伊朗、俄羅斯、北韓同級。同時國會亦通過撥款調查香港官員及商人曾否干犯反人類罪、滅絕罪、戰爭罪等等國際刑事罪行。看來是為與中國脫鉤鋪路，聯繫匯率能否維持成為疑問。而一旦香港聯繫匯率脫鉤，對中國經濟的影響也就顯而易見。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n相關截圖: <a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWNkZmNlNjM5OTRmOGIxYmM1MmRiLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMTk4JmhlaWdodD04NDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5cdfce63994f8b1bc52db.png?width=1198&amp;height=840\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5cdfce63994f8b1bc52db.png?width=1198&amp;height=840\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5cdfce63994f8b1bc52db.png?width=1198&amp;height=840\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTc1MTU1MWJjZTI2ZDJkODcwOGM4LnBuZz93aWR0aD02ODgmaGVpZ2h0PTcyOA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1751551bce26d2d8708c8.png?width=688&amp;height=728\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1751551bce26d2d8708c8.png?width=688&amp;height=728\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1751551bce26d2d8708c8.png?width=688&amp;height=728\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n參考資料: <a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY29uZ3Jlc3MuZ292L2JpbGwvMTE4dGgtY29uZ3Jlc3MvaG91c2UtYmlsbC8yNjcwL3RleHQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/118th-congress/house-bill/2670/text\">草案最終版本</a> </div>",
